Requires: httpd >= 2.0.52
Requires: mod_perl
Requires: perl >= 2:5.8.0
Requires: perl(DBI) perl(Data::ShowTable) perl(Unicode::String)
Requires: perl(DBD::mysql) perl(MIME::Base64) perl(Net::SMTP)
